      <title>谷歌整合团队，旨在更快地开发人工智能产品</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/google-consolidates-teams-with-aim-to-create-ai-products-faster</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Alphabet Inc.首席执行官桑达尔·皮查伊(Sundar Pichai)宣布对谷歌工作团队结构进行调整，称此举将帮助该公司更快、更高效地开发人工智能产品和服务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/google-consolidates-teams-with-aim-to-create-ai-products-faster</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 19:30:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
